{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lesson-template-js","path":"/macros","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>This is where things can get fun.  Also, they are a bit psychologically\nweird...  Meaning, you will find yourself feeling like you don't know how to do\nthe most basic of moves.  If this happens, its ok.  Its called Macro Pressure.</p>\n<h3 id=\"what-is-a-macro\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-is-a-macro\" aria-label=\"what is a macro permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What is a Macro</h3>\n<p>A macro simply plays text as motions, inputs, and commands.</p>\n<h4 id=\"let-me-show-you\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#let-me-show-you\" aria-label=\"let me show you permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Let me show you!</h4>\n<p>I remember my first macro like it was yesterday.....</p>\n<h4 id=\"example-time\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#example-time\" aria-label=\"example time permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"tru